data.description: HUGE Price improvement!!! SPECTACULAR 3 YEAR OLD IN GROUND GUNITE GAS HEATED POOL/SPA and an almost new home located in a fantastic neighborhood on a quiet cul-de-sac is ready and waiting for one fortunate buyer!!  This lovely family home features close to 2300 sq ft of spacious living with a wonderful open floor plan!!  Enter into a formal living room (that is currently set up as a 5th bedroom,) and then step into your gourmet chef's kitchen with a separate dining area that opens up to your commodious family room!! The kitchen is stunning with espresso wood cabinetry, white quartz countertops and upgraded stainless steel appliances!! Then head upstairs to your 4 generously sized bedrooms upstairs including a master bedroom with a dreamy en suite that boasts a separate shower and tub, double sinks and walk in closet!! There are also 2 1/2 baths and a super convenient upstairs laundry room!! Then get ready to go see your amazing entertainer's backyard complete with a 3 year old absolutely spectacular IGG POOL/SPA with waterfalls, bouquet stone veneer and all newer pool equipment including a gas heater too!! You are sure to fall in love with your low maintenance backyard that is all concrete in the back and side yards, includes a raised patio area, a doggie run and wrought iron gate too!! Can you believe there is even paved RV access with double wood gate and appealing all rock landscaping in the front yard?? You will also have your own water softener system by ECOWATER that is completely paid for!!! This POOL/SPA home is a rare find so hurry to schedule your own private tour before it is sold!!!
